Error 1:-

Missing required argument $eventPrefix of Sales\Menu\Model\ResourceModel\Dropdowns\Grid\Collection

Error 2: - 


Class does not exists

This error occurs when because the filename doesn't match with the class name.

Example:- Filename is :- Dropdowns.php


<?php


namespace Sales\Menu\Model\ResourceModel;

use Magento\Framework\Model\ResourceModel\Db\AbstractDb;

class Label extends AbstractDb
{
    /**
     * Define main table
     */
    protected function _construct()
    {
        $this->_init('refund_request_dropdown_options', 'id');
    }
}

You can see the line number 22 that the file name is not matching with class you created. So, please cross the check filename and class name when you 
get these type of error.
